1) Profile Creator : Creates profiles for macOS, iOS, tvOS

https://github.com/ProfileCreator/ProfileCreator

2) iMazing Profile Editor: Creates Profiles for macOS, iOS, tvOS
  - Sometimes this works better than Profile Creator 

https://imazing.com/profile-editor

2) PPPC-Utility: Creates Privacy Preferences Policy Control payloads for macOS

  https://github.com/jamf/PPPC-Utility


3) Script2pkg: Helps create payload-free packages for macOS
  - Useful for deploying a script as a package.

https://github.com/SAP/script-to-package-tool-for-macos

4)Suspicious Package
  - Inspects .pkgs, useful for detecting malicious packages and also seeing how one is created

https://mothersruin.com/software/SuspiciousPackage/

5) Payload-Free-Package-Creator
  -is an Automator application that uses AppleScript, shell scripting and pkgbuild behind the scenes to create payload-free packages. 

https://github.com/rtrouton/Payload-Free-Package-Creator

5) PlistEdit pro ($)
  - Edits and creates plist files
https://www.fatcatsoftware.com/plisteditpro/

6) Jamf Composer
  - Creates packages for installation
